trends: There has been one other sighting in Sturgeon Bay
There were no other sightings in Sturgeon Bay on or around October 12th 2013
Summary: Solid brite white light moving fast
divs: Sighting DetailsStepped outside for a cigarette, and happened to walk out towards road when my eye was drawn to a bright white light of triple intensity of normal star moving rapidly toward the north. thought for a second or two that it was an aircraft, until I realized that there were no tell-tail flashes of wing or tail strobes. ran inside to get cameraphone, and attempted to film object - however due to darkness am unsure whether video will show anything. roughly 10 seconds after beginning to film, light faded out. from first sighting it till it faded out was aprox. 45 seconds. will work on video and attempt to enhance brightness.
